# ============================================================
# CORE PHILOSOPHY
# ============================================================

## Universal Theory of Flow
Topology precedes dynamics at every scale.
Form is not static shape — it is an anticipatory script.
Knots, folds, slip knots, and nested knots are the universal
grammar of how systems pre-wire the paths along which forces,
signals, and functions move.

See: Research/universal-theory-of-flow.md
See: Technology/docs/Propulsion_Theory.md

## Hackerwatch Sovereign
We watch. We log. We signal. We do not attack.
Defense is dismantling the means — not killing the actors.
Read-only posture. Love-based vigilance.

See: SECURITY&DEFENSE/

## Hi Ho Hi Ho
We keep marching. Steady, warm, purposeful.
No scatter. No panic. Structured forward motion.

