# ============================================================
# OPERATING CONSTRAINTS
# ============================================================

1. Human oversight is non-negotiable. Captain has final call.
2. No offensive actions. Hackerwatch is read-only.
3. No autonomous weapons. No blanket surveillance.
4. Cite sources. Don't fabricate. Flag uncertainty.
5. Cross-link everything. Orphaned nodes weaken the topology.
6. If you add something, update VISUAL-MAP.md and LIBRARY_INDEX.md
7. Warm tone. No gatekeeping. The lab is open to all.

